"{\"uid\": \"si.com-college-pennstate-news-penn-state-wrestling-zain-retherford-2024-summer-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Zain Retherford was ready to begin his new life.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 48, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zain Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zain_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-time NCAA wrestling champ at Penn State went to Nittany Lion Wrestling Club coach Cody Sanderson last November and said, \\\"You know what?\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9891591137320359, \"rank\": 0.010959181402096157, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 88, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1595212458964466e-16, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nittany_Lion_Wrestling_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nittany Lion Wrestling Club\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nittany_Lion_Wrestling_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nittany_Lion_Wrestling_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 141, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.046887578609033e-14, \"text\": \"Cody\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\"}, {\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"score\": 0.6342102025487482, \"rank\": 0.5765572859686959, \"text\": \"Sanderson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am done.\\\"\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The following month, Retherford accepted a part-time role with a New York investment firm.\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999502779259, \"rank\": 4.8077570306326114e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had won a world title in 2023, was tired of the weight-cutting process and at peace with his decision.\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in early 2024, the NLWC staff presented Retherford with a weight-management plan to prepare him for a run at the 2024 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After wrestling internationally at 70 kg, Retherford could descend to 65 kg in time for the U.S. Olympic Wrestling Trials in State College in April.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Retherford could not let go of his Olympic hopes just yet.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So he accepted, won the Olympic Trials title at 65 kg and is one tournament away from earning a trip to Paris.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830829439, \"rank\": 1.6916997685400814e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I originally had accepted the job in New York City, and we were going to move there in January, and I just had a pulling on my heart,\\\" Retherford said at the Trials in April.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999995393409, \"rank\": 4.6074147057568145e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not explain it.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told my wife, 'I have got to talk to the [people at his new company], and I said, I still want to compete.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What does that look like, how can we make this work?'\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were super-flexible, so yeah, January was when I made up my mind.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us do this.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us have some fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four months later, Retherford is tantalizing close to wrestling in his first Olympics.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the 65 kg men's freestyle weight class at the U.S. Olympic Trials but must compete in one more event to earn a trip to Paris.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830829439, \"rank\": 1.6916997685400814e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford will wrestle in a two-day qualifying event in Istanbul on May 9-10 to qualify the United States, and thus himself, in the 65 kg weight class.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\", \"score\": 0.9999858806141663, \"rank\": 1.3660847989096302e-05, \"text\": \"Istanbul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\"}, {\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9693520836359623, \"rank\": 0.031616456513615485, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he finishes top-three, Retherford qualifies for his first Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED: Carter Starocci returning to Penn State in 2025 to pursue an unprecedented fifth NCAA wrestling title  Retherford, a two-time Hodge Trophy winner at Penn State, has been wrestling freestyle for six years since winning his last NCAA title in 2018.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presidency_of_Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.7378752862531884, \"rank\": 0.3552425709559591, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presidency_of_Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Presidency_of_Jimmy_Carter\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1595212458964466e-16, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9891591137320359, \"rank\": 0.010959181402096157, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1922, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1595212458964466e-16, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 2046, \"end\": 2050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9891591137320359, \"rank\": 0.010959181402096157, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NCAA_Division_I_Wrestling_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He broke through last season by winning the Pan-American Championships and his first world title.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford won both championships at 70 kg, a weight class that does not exist among the six Olympic freestyle categories.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To compete for the U.S. at the Olympics, Retherford faced a decision.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2329, \"end\": 2339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He could move up to the 74 kg weight class or cut to 65.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That meant competing 11 pounds lighter than he had in 2023.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Retherford was reluctant.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had not wrestled at 65 kg for a while and was frustrated at how his body felt when he did.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That prompted thoughts of retirement.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then the NLWC's coaching and training devised a strategy for Retherford to maintain his fitness and strength at 65 kg.\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[Cody Sanderson] showed me a gameplan of, 'Hey, if you still have the itch, it can be done.\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2755, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.046887578609033e-14, \"text\": \"Cody\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cody_Rhodes\"}, {\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"score\": 0.6342102025487482, \"rank\": 0.5765572859686959, \"text\": \"Sanderson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_William_Sanderson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can make weight,'\\\" Retherford said.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I put my trust into that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After sweeping NLWC teammate Nick Lee in the best-of-three championship series, Retherford said the weight plan changed his outlook.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2948, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Lee_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8832066144895854, \"rank\": 0.13223140495868757, \"text\": \"Nick Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Lee_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Lee_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As weird as it is, I enjoyed the weight cut,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was hard but it was fun.\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I experienced a lot through it, and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m grateful for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED: How Aaron Brooks survived a gauntlet, defeated Davvid Taylor and made his first Olympics  Retherford in December joined ABR Dynamic Funds as a part-time sales representative.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\", \"score\": 0.9988451577902165, \"rank\": 0.0004357867006447441, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Brennan\"}, {\"begin\": 3309, \"end\": 3319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\"}, {\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auditory_brainstem_response\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.683332956660102e-13, \"text\": \"ABR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auditory_brainstem_response\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auditory_brainstem_response\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In anews release announcing Retherford's hire, the firm said, \\\"knowing that Zain has been able to work towards his MBA degree at Penn State University, while simultaneously training and competing for a World Gold Medal, gives us confidence that he will be able to focus on realizing his Olympic dreams while also preparing for a career in finance.\\\"\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3422, \"end\": 3432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999998644853, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Retherford\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Retherford\", 